    "longBusinessSummary": "Vietnam Asia Commercial Joint Stock Bank provides banking products and services in Vietnam. It offers current, escrow, and savings accounts; term deposits; and loans, including real estate, home, secured consumer, auto, home construction and renovation, and working capital loans, as well as business loans to invest in fixed assets, and loans secured by financial instruments and deposits. The company also provides export business, and medium- and long-term financing; car, private apartment/house, health and casualty, global travel, personal loan, and life insurance products; cash collection and payment services; trade finance services; guarantees; and bill payment, remittance, international and domestic fund transfer, treasury, and international fund receipt services. In addition, it conducts banking transactions, including mobilizing and receiving short, medium, and long-term deposits; foreign exchange transactions; and discounting commercial papers, bonds, and other valuable papers. Further, the company offers cards; mobile, personal internet, corporate internet, and SMS banking services; debt management and asset exploitation services; electronic wallets; and ATM, brokerage, and other banking services. The company was incorporated in 2003 and is headquartered in Hanoi, Vietnam.",
